data.description: Welcome to your dream home located at 11358 State Highway 110 N in the vibrant city of Tyler, TX! This magnificent house is now available for sale, offering you the perfect blend of modern comfort and scenic tranquility. With four spacious bedrooms and two bathrooms, this home provides ample space for you and your loved ones. The open floor plan creates a seamless flow throughout the 1,669 square feet of living space, giving you the freedom to design and decorate according to your unique taste. The windows allow natural light to flood each room, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The well-appointed kitchen features sleek countertops, modern appliances, and plenty of storage space, making it a true chef's delight. Situated on a generous 1.3-acre lot with no restrictions, this property offers endless possibilities. Whether you envision hosting summer BBQs on the expansive backyard or creating your own private oasis, you'll have the space to turn your dreams into reality. And with the convenience of being just outside the city limits, you can enjoy both privacy and easy access to all that Tyler/Lindale has to offer. Additionally, this property boasts ample parking spaces for family and guests. Whether you have multiple vehicles or simply need room for recreational vehicles, this house has you covered. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to make 11358 State Highway 110 N your forever home. Call today to schedule a showing and experience the charm and beauty that awaits you in this exceptional property.
